Wash the @tomatoes{200%g} and slice them into chunks, if they are cherry tomatoes, you can just halve them. Peel the @red onions{10%g} and slice them into thin rings, which you can then halve. Wash the @coriander{10%g} and chop coarsely. Mix the tomatoes, onion and coriander in a bowl and season with @salt{1/4%tsp}, pepper, a splash of olive oil and @Worcester sauce{10%g}. Enjoy as a simple side salad with any meal.
